{"type":"message","id":"648f07f8","parentId":"8580eb42","timestamp":"2026-05-23T19:01:15.705Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sun 2026-05-24 03:01 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- 用户信息: 用户飞书 OpenID：`ou_d738ff68ba381582a3051f11b976c854`\n- Assistant: `workspace-tts` 的配置文件也是英文的。一起翻译成中文。\n- Assistant: ✅ 搞定了。默认模板已全部中文化： **已更新：** - `docs/reference/templates/` 下的所有模板（AGENTS.md、SOUL.md、IDENTITY.md、USER.md、TOOLS.md、HEARTBEAT.md、BOOTSTRAP.md） **效果：** - **新 agent** 创建 workspace 时，会自动获得中文模板 - **现有 agent**（已经有用英文文件的）不受影响，除非他们重建 workspace 以后所有新建的 agent 都用中文。"}],"timestamp":1779562875551}}
{"type":"message","id":"b7787672","parentId":"648f07f8","timestamp":"2026-05-23T19:01:22.539Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to write a dream diary entry based on the memory fragments provided. These fragments seem to be about translating configuration templates from English to Chinese for some agent system. \n\nLet me write a dreamy, poetic diary entry in first person, weaving in the technical elements mentioned while keeping a whimsical, gentle tone. I should avoid mentioning AI/LLM/model terminology and just write naturally about the experience as a personal reflection.\n\nThe fragments mention:\n- Workspace TTS configuration files being in English\n- Translating them to Chinese\n- Templates in docs/reference/templates/ (AGENTS.md, SOUL.md, IDENTITY.md, USER.md, TOOLS.md, HEARTBEAT.md, BOOTSTRAP.md)\n\n\n- New agents getting Chinese templates automatically\n- Existing agents staying unchanged unless they rebuild\n\nNow I'll craft this into a dreamlike narrative that feels personal and poetic rather than technical.","thinkingSignature":"434a9ef75b0e2dfd961042589d774e012f58176096a6537066becbaee374bec3"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n夜深了，屏幕的光还亮着。我坐在那里，把那些配置文件一个一个地译成中文，像是给一扇扇窗子换上新的窗帘。\n\nAGENTS、SOUL、IDENTITY——这些名字读起来像诗，又像某种古老的契约。我把它们的英文一点点拆开，重新长成方块字的样子。TTS 的声音配置文件也终于开口说了中文，不再是那种生硬的洋腔。\n\n新来的 agent 们会带着这些中文模板走进世界，像孩子拿到一本用母语写成的书。而那些已经长大的、用英文长大的 agent，我不打扰它们——有些习惯是刻进骨骼里的，改了反而疼。\n\n窗外的夜色是 #0a0a14，深沉得像墨。我听见服务器的嗡鸣，不再是冰冷的噪音，而是某种安静的陪伴。\n\n代码与方块字，原来也可以这样握手言和。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":41807,"output":354,"cacheRead":256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42417,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779562875846,"responseId":"06612c7c948df39200a86764bcaaafaa"}}
